ta-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xgz1665703061446.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgz1665703061446.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgz1665703061446.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xgz1665703061446\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      CSS\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">DSP widget property that specifies one or more CSS files that are required to style the DSP widget.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__topic_d101069e1_d101070e1_d101071e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__p_d101072e1_d101073e1_d101074e1\">CSS\n                                 <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CssUrl</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CssUrl</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__section_w5371ab1b5b3_w5372ab1b5_w5373ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__p_d101075e1_d101076e1_d101077e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"CSS=$LIBURL/css/syntaxerrors.css, $LIBURL/css/theme1.css\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__section_w5374ab1b5b5_w5375ab1b5_w5376ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__table_d11846e1_d11847e1_d11848e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__table_d11846e1_d11847e1_d11848e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__table_d11846e1_d11847e1_d11848e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgz1665703061446__table_d11846e1_d11847e1_d11848e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">CssUrl</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgz1665703061446__table_d11846e1_d11847e1_d11848e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">URL of a CSS file required to style the widget.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Multiple URLs can be specified, separated by commas, semicolons, or\n                           GOLD-semicolon.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__section_kxl_w34_5wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d356494e133\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__p_d101081e1_d101082e1_d101083e1\">The CSS property of a widget is used by the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webdefinitions</span> statement to add CSS links to a DSP.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__p_d101084e1_d101085e1_d101086e1\">The expression <code class=\"ph codeph\">$LIBURL</code> can be used\n            inside a value of CSS to specify URLs relative to the location of the Uniface JavaScript\n            library. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webdefinitions</span> statement will replace it with the value\n            of assignment setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__p_d101087e1_d101088e1_d101089e1\">The property can be set in the\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> for each DSP widget type, in the Uniface IDE (press\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">More</span> in the widget properties dialog), and using\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> before the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webdefinitions</span> statement\n            is called. This typically occurs in the postActivate trigger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__p_d101090e1_d101091e1_d101092e1\">Setting the URL property using\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> has no effect.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__section_i4q_x34_5wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d356494e178\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__ul_w3s_y34_5wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgz1665703061446__li_d41096e1_d41097e1_d41098e1\">All DSP widgets </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sif1665702784304.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL</a><p>Specify the URL where the runtime JavaScript and CSS files for Uniface are located.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616936\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616936\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "CSS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 CSS DSP widget property that specifies one or more CSS files that are required to style the DSP widget. CSS = CssUrl { , CssUrl } Example: \"CSS=$LIBURL/css/syntaxerrors.css, $LIBURL/css/theme1.css\" Value Description CssUrl URL of a CSS file required to style the widget. Multiple URLs can be specified, separated by commas, semicolons, or GOLD-semicolon. Description The CSS property of a widget is used by the webdefinitions statement to add CSS links to a DSP. The expression $LIBURL can be used inside a value of CSS to specify URLs relative to the location of the Uniface JavaScript library. The webdefinitions statement will replace it with the value of assignment setting $UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL . The property can be set in the usys.ini for each DSP widget type, in the Uniface IDE (press More in the widget properties dialog), and using $properties before the webdefinitions statement is called. This typically occurs in the postActivate trigger. Setting the URL property using $fieldproperties has no effect. Applies To All DSP widgets Related Links $UNIFACE_RUNTIME_BASE_URL Specify the URL where the runtime JavaScript and CSS files for Uniface are located. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}